name: Ayu Ting Ting
description: '''Ayu Rosmalina''' (born {{Birth date |1992|6|20|}}), better known by her stage name '''Ayu Ting Ting''', is an Indonesian singer and presenter. One of Indonesia's [[dangdut]] [[diva]]s, she rose to fame following the sudden virality of her song ''"Alamat Palsu"'' ("Fake Address") in 2011. Her stage name "Ting Ting" means "virgin" in Indonesian.{{sfn|Ariwibowo 2011, Ayu Ting Ting}}
